-- France Telecom's Orange Mobile-Phone Unit Aims to Double Its Customer Base
-- B y   N i c k y   S m i t h
-- 2010-11-10T16:11:03Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-10/france-telecom-s-orange-unit-aims-to-double-africa-revenue.html
(Corrects to say company plans to double customer base in
first paragraph.)  France Telecom SA’s Orange mobile-
phone unit intends to double its customer base, Executive Vice
President for Africa, Middle East and Asia  Marc Rennard  said.  The company’s goal is to reach 300 million customers by
2015, 55 million of which are in the Middle East and Africa, he
said at a conference in Cape Town today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
